ComicInfo.Summary: Odyssey's End [Part 1]: With the Enterprise on a mission to contain a massive star that is about to go hyper-nova, Captain Kirk is uneasy over his pending promotion to admiral. The mission is interrupted when they receive a Tholian distress call from a planet that was believed to be uninhabited.
